5Th Avenue Perfume by Elizabeth Arden, 5th Avenue by Elizabeth Arden is a perfume that evokes a refreshed feeling of spring with its clean, distinct aromas. The base notes are composed of iris, vanilla, amber, sandalwood and Tibetan musk, which situate this perfume with a comforting yet sharp mood

Lanvin Cologne by Lanvin, Lanvin is a sparkling yet refined cologne for the modern man. Launched in 1997, the fragrance features a mix of refreshing ingredients to keep you energized all day. Neroli, bergamot, and mandarin orange start the scent with an invigorating blend of citrus fruits. Lavender infuses them with a sprig of green earthiness. The middle notes are just as sharp. Pepper, sage, mint, and cardamom lend both warm and cool tones of spice. The smooth base features sandalwood, amber, vanilla, and musk, which mix together for a sweet, sensual vibe. Wear this exhilarating cologne whenever you need an aromatic burst of energy.


Jeanne Lanvin established her famed fashion brand in 1889. She originally created one-of-a-kind clothes for her daughter. These designs caught the eye of wealthy parents, who requested versions for their own children. She then began making clothes for the parents. The company is the oldest fashion house in France.

Product_Name: Bourjois Little Round Pot Blusher - 34 Rose d'or / 2.5 g
Product_Descriptions:
Blushing beauty at your fingertips!

Bourjois Little Round Pot Blusher has been keeping women beautiful for generations. Made in an exclusive baked technology process, its incredibly transparent & light texture formula is easy to apply and blends impeccably. One stroke of the brush reveals the irresistible rose scented aroma. Its built-in mirror and brush are perfect for touch-ups on the go!

For glamorous colour, this ultra-fine powder blush is a must-have in your bag of beauty tricks. 

Smile and apply the blush on your cheekbones with circular movements. Then stretch up to the temples. 

Exists in 17 shades from the most transparent pearly effect to a subtle matte finish.

Famous for almost 150 years, the adorable Bourjois Little Round Pot Blushers have been in the vanity bags of stylish women for generations.


Ready to play with make-up? In Paris, beauty is a game, never a chore. Bourjois makes it easy to create chic looks for eyes, lips, face and nails, all with an effortless Parisian twist. Say Bonjour to beauty with ?joie de vivre?!

Eclat D'arpege Perfume by Lanvin, Eclat D'Arpege is a womens floral fruity scent with floral, fresh, green, musky, and fruity main accords. Presented in 2002, this fragrance was developed by perfumer Karine Dubreuil of Mane. At the top are notes of Sicilian lemon and green lilac. In the middle are wisteria blossom, red peony, and peach blossom notes. Musk, amber, and cedar make up the base notes. The perfume has soft sillage and moderate longevity, making it ideal for spring and summer day wear.


Lanvin was founded in 1889 by designer Jeanne-Marie Lanvin in Paris, France when she started making clothes for her daughter. It is known as the oldest fashion house in France. Lanvin was known as one of the most highly influential designers of her time, in the 1920s and 1930s. She launched her perfume line in 1924, with Arpege becoming the brand???s signature fragrance in 1927. The company is privately owned by the Harmonie S.F. investor group and the fragrance license is held by Inter Parfums

Inspired by feminine sensuality, Calvin Klein Euphoria Eau de Toilette bursts with luscious, dewy freshness. Entwining top notes of sparkling mirabelle plum with a radiant orchid base and a warm and airy vanilla trail, this amber gourmand Calvin Klein scent conjures deliciously addictive desire.


Expressing the essence of feminine sensuality and desire, Calvin Klein Euphoria Eau de Toilette is a tempting amber gourmand with deliciously seductive notes of fresh fruit and florals, and a mesmerizing and addictive vanilla accord finish. Youthful and feminine, luscious yet weightless, Calvin Klein Euphoria Eau de Toilette draws inspiration from the ripe dewiness of the original Calvin Klein Euphoria signature fragrance, created in 2005. A modern interpretation, this passionate and provocative CK scent entwines sparkling top notes of mirabelle plum with a radiant orchid and rose essential base to create an intoxicating and mouthwatering succulence. A trail of airy vanilla balances this Calvin Klein scent's delicious vibrance with an enticing and comforting warmth. The perfect scent for any occasion. Made with natural ingredients including rose essential-a responsibly sourced, certified Fair Trade extract-this Calvin Klein scent is housed in an updated clear glass version of the signature bottle, designed to reveal the gorgeous perfume's delicate, dew-inspired pink hue.

Oud Malaki by Chopard is an oriental fragrance. This Chopard Perfume is suitable for men. Enjoy the dark, seductive spices of Oud Malaki by Chopard for Men. This rich fragrance is signed by perfumer Dominique Ropion, uplifts oud. The journey of this oriental fragrance starts with luminous accords of grapefruit in the very top of the composition, along with an aromatic blend of artemisia and lavender. The heart allures you with its leather accords combined with tobacco and spices. Finally, the base settles with oud, ambergris, and mysterious woody notes. The perfect blend of these notes mesmerizes you with its exhilarating fragrance.

Product_Name: The Body Set Hair Brush With Rubber Coating

Product_Descriptions:
Why compromise between beauty and care? Meet the first-ever long-wear polish, infused with Keratin, Jojoba Oil & Vitamin E.


FEATURES & BENEFITS






More brush, better precision: New ergonomic, curve-hugging brush that consumers and professionals love.Your favourite long-lasting colour: A beautiful chip-resistant wear that lasts 7 days, now infused with Vitamin E, Keratin & Jojoba Oil.New and more efficient formula: New formula thickens less over time, allowing for a simple 2-step application for a faster nail service.








HOW TO USE






Must be used as a system: Color = Adhesion + Top Coat = Time-enhanced durability.Perform P.E.P. to ensure the nail is thoroughly cleansed and prepared.Shake vigorously to blend.Apply two thin layers of VINYLUX™ Weekly Polish.Finish with one layer of VINYLUX™ Weekly Polish Top Coat.


INGREDIENTS






Butyl Acetate, Ethyl Acetate, Nitrocellulose, Acetyl Tributyl Citrate, Isopropyl Alcohol, Adipic Acid/Neopentyl Glycol/Trimellitic Anhydride Copolymer, Glycidoxypropyl Polysilsesquioxane, Stearalkonium Bentonite, Benzophenone-1, Diacetone Alcohol, Hydrolyzed Keratin, Hydroxydodecyl Hydroxyethyl Ethylenediamine/Methyl Acrylate Dendrimer, Propylene Carbonate, Silica, Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil, Styrene/Acrylates Copolymer, Tocopheryl Acetate. May Contain: Titanium Dioxide, Styrene/Acrylates Copolymer, Benzophenone-1, N-Butyl Alcohol, Silica, Tin Oxide, Barium Sulfate, Colophonium (Rosin) (Colophane), Calcium Aluminum Borosilicate, Mica, Dimethicone, Trimethylsiloxysilicate, Synthetic Fluorphlogopite, Calcium Sodium Borosilicate, Polyethylene Terephthalate, Acrylates Copolymer, Diacetone Alcohol, Propylene Carbonate Colorants.

Product_Name: Bourjois Rouge Velvet The Lipstick - 01 Hey Nude / 2.4g
Product_Descriptions:
Looking to wow with a bold matte lipstick that won?t smudge?

Meet Bourjois Rouge Velvet The Lipstick, a gorgeous long-wearing lipstick that will never dry out lips! The secret of its exclusive formula is the moisturising complex that combines hydrating waxes with light oils and rich pigments for an irresistible velvety soft finish that pops.

When you want a precise lipstick with intense matte colour that lasts long and feels light, just one swipe of Rouge Velvet The Lipstick will give your lips up to 24 hours of full-on glamour. 

For intense colour in one stroke with a precise and flawless finish, Rouge Edition Velvet The Lipstick is an essential addition to your make-up collection!


Ready to play with make-up? In Paris, beauty is a game, never a chore. Bourjois makes it easy to create chic looks for eyes, lips, face and nails, all with an effortless Parisian twist. Say Bonjour to beauty with ?joie de vivre?!

Product_Name: Garnier Micellar Oil-Infused Cleansing Water - 400 ML
Product_Descriptions:
For the first time, Garnier introduces a new generation in removing make-up with a bi-phase formula enriched with micelles and nourishing Argan oil, especially designed to capture heavy bold makeup from the skin and remove it easily.

Once the two are mixed, the two phases become active and instantly dissolve all types of make-up, impurities and pollution.

Cleanse and nourish the feel of skin, in one step without rinsing.

Dermatologically and ophthalmologically tested.

Product_Name: Pupa Never Without All In One Face Palette - 001-Light Skin
Product_Descriptions:
The compact and practical "survival" palette. Contains 5 textures for creating complete face make-up or on-the-go retouching.
1. CREAM CONCEALER: corrects small imperfections and brightens the eye area and shaded areas of the face, giving the complexion a fresh and radiant appearance.
2. POWDER: fixes the make-up and mattifies the shiny areas of the face.
3. CONTOURING BRONZER: sculpts the facial features for a natural tan effect.
4. BLUSH: tints cheeks and cheekbones with a touch of colour.
5. FACE HIGHLIGHTER: creates gentle hints of light on the facial contours.
Dermatologically tested
Paraben Free
Made in Italy

Discover L'Oréal Paris Elvive Full Resist conditioner that cleanses the scalp & nourishes the root, leaving hair stronger & more resistant to hair fall.


Weak hair lacks essential nutrients. When fragile at the root, it has poor resistance to daily tortures such as washing, brushing and styling, which can lead to hair breaking and falling. Rebuild your hair strength with Elvive Full Resist Anti-Breakage Fragile Hair Conditioner. Our reinforcing formula charged with supplements [ biotin + vitamin B5 + arginine] works in affinity with the hair fibre from root to tip, leaving hair stronger and more resistant to hair fall.


More sustainable: Our bottle is made of 100% recycled plastic and is 100% recyclable.

The results?

1) Rebuilt fibers

2) Strength

3) Vitality

4) Silkiness

and 5) Shine.

Our strengthening system with Protein + Ceramide helps fortify each strand, reinforcing hair fiber and sealing-in nourishment. For best results, use L’Oréal Paris Total Repair 5 shampoo and conditioner together.


*When using complete system of shampoo, conditioner, and treatment.

Trussardi Black Extreme Cologne by Trussardi, An enticing and sophisticated scent for men, Trussardi Black Extreme was released in 2014. This cologne was created with the help of perfumer Aurelien Guichard. Italian lemon, galbanum, cypress and marine accord are the top notes. Cypress offers a fresh, green smell and galbanum gives the scent a pleasant musk. Middle notes include black plum, violet leaf and Italian orris. The unique base boasts hints of vetiver, black leather and patchouli. Looking for something to impress a special someone on that first date? Look no further.


Trussardi has grown immensely over the 20th century. It began as a glove-making company in 1910, spearheaded by a man named Dante. Dante???s grandson Nicola has inherited the design house, which has grown to be well-known for its classy leather accessories. Relevant and modern fashion remains a priority in their creations, but so does authenticity.


This cologne is preferable for evening wear and ideal for the crisp season of Autumn.

Mauboussin Pour Lui In Black Cologne by Mauboussin, Mauboussin Pour Lui In Black is a woody oriental fragrance for men by Mauboussin. Introduced in 2015 and created by Nathalie Feisthauer, this fragrance is enticingly powerful, yet charming. This fragrance opens with notes of juicy mandarin orange, cool mint and salted caramel butter. Next, the green tinged heart notes include black violet, sage and cedar. The base notes of this fragrance are Gaiac wood, beonzoin and patchouli. Gaiac wood is a little smoky and a little sweet, benzoin is warm and comforting and partchouli is earthy and sweet.


Mauboussin is a French company that has produced fine jewelry since 1827. During the century following its founding, Mauboussin became well known for its unique, artistic jewelry designs and now is best known for its stunning Art Deco era creations. During the 1920s, the jewelry entered a number of exhibitions and in 1925, won the prestigious Gold award at the Exposition des Arts D‹¨«?®coratifs in Paris. Mauboussin diversified into fragrances in 2000.

Product_Name: Giorgio Armani Si Intense Femme Edp - 50Ml
Product_Descriptions:
Armani Si was launched in 2013 as a sweet scent of cassis, rose and vanilla. In 2014, Armani introduces its enhanced version Armani Si Eau de Parfum Intense. The new version is designed for a strong and passionate woman who is brave and not afraid to take risks. Such woman is conceived as very charismatic, confident, independent and sophisticated.

"Denser" and richer than the original, Si Intense is described as a modern chypre fragrance. It opens with accords of cassis and black currant heart extract. There are also fresh notes of mandarin and bergamot with a silky touch of freesia. The heart develops with essence of May rose and neroli absolute, with additional accords of davana and osmanthus. The base features patchouli, vanilla, ambroxan and woody notes.

The face of the perfume is actress Cate Blanchett. The fragrance is available as 30, 50 and 100 ml Eau de Parfum.

Product_Name: Giorgio Armani Eau De Nuit Homme Edt - 100Ml
Product_Descriptions:
Fashion house Armani presented its first masculine fragrance Eau Pour Homme in 1984. Sharp, strong, citrusy and aromatic, this one has become a classic among mens fragrances. Almost 30 years later, in February the 2013, Armani launches a new version of Eau Pour Homme and a brand new nocturnal edition Eau de Nuit.

Eau de Nuit, dark and opulent, combines notes of spices, citruses, cedar and iris. The composition is warmer and more sensual than the debut. It opens with accords of bergamot and pink pepper. Spicy notes of cardamom and nutmeg form the heart of the perfume together with flowers of iris and heliotrope. The base consists of cedar, tonka and amber.

Jimmy Choo Perfume by Jimmy Choo, Launched in 2011, Jimmy Choo is an empowering and sensual scent for the woman who knows what she wants. This sophisticated and seductive fragrance makes for the perfect accessory when you desire to hold someone???s attention. Wear it casually during the day or throughout the evening when you are looking for fun. The top notes pull forward with mandarin orange, pear and green notes. The heart notes focus on the beauty of the orchid. The base is a perfect mixture of patchouli and toffee. With a generous longevity and sillage, this perfume can make a lasting impression.


Born in Penang, Malaysia, Jimmy Choo is perhaps best known for his handmade shoes for women. Learning the craft from his father, he made his first shoe at 11. He later moved to London to study, and he opened his first shoe shop in a converted hospital building in 1986. After his designs began generating a buzz, he co-founded his eponymous fashion label in 1996 with Tamara Mellon, a Vogue Magazine editor.

Powerful, vigorous, and fiery, nature reveals itself (again) with a vengeance. Molten lava pours expressively from a volcano. Fusion d’Issey transforms this eruption of energy into a bold, nuanced composition, giving rise to a creative, endemic nature. Depth, tension, and power for a distinctive fragrance.
Master Perfumer Nathalie Lorson composed Fusion d’Issey, a fougère for men with solar and mineral notes. A rewriting of a masculine classic. A play on contrasts between the cold and the heat of warming spices.
For the cool aspect, the sparkling brightness of lemon is paired with the milky sweetness of coconut water, a long-lasting solar scent. Plunging into the heart of the volcano to encounter the mineral and uncover the roundness of ambrox. In an ethereal whisper, essence of fresh rosemary, geranium, and cardamom
(both cool and blazing) dissipate, filling the surroundings with their trailing scent. Underlying the notion of fusion is the choice of warm, volcanic wood featuring patchouli. For Nathalie
Lorson, Fusion d’Issey “shows an incandescent quality”. A new masculinity, heat and cold to express the idea of the quintessence of molten rock. Overflowing with energy and vitality, Fusion d’Issey, a fragrance for daring adventures.

Eye Treatment

Modern Muse Perfume by Estee Lauder, Be the belle of the ball in the luscious and dignified Modern Muse, a sensational women's fragrance . This tantalizing elixir blends citrus, floral and earthy accords for a sweet and seductive perfume that's at once both soft and feminine as well as daring and sexy. The top note of citrus mandarin orange offers an eye-opening start that's vibrant and appealing. Heart notes of Chinese jasmine, Sambac jasmine, light honeysuckle, tuberose, fresh white lily and fragrant flower petals enhance the aroma with their decadent floral bouquet for a stunning appeal. Finally, base notes of smooth Madagascar vanilla, sensual musk, golden amber, heady patchouli, green patchouli leaf and various woody tones wrap up the scent for a high-quality, opulent perfume you'll be hard-pressed to wash away from your skin.

Dent De Lait Perfume by Serge Lutens, A curious concoction born from contrasts, Dent De Lait saw its first release in 2017. This unisex fragrance defies a straightforward description; it can be called a floral, nutty accord, but that doesn???t fully capture what it is. Almond milk and metallic notes are the two defining aspects at work here, accented by cashmeran, coconut and heliotrope. Far from being a discordant clash of opposing elements, the result is tangy but with a clean, gentle side, hard to place yet somehow familiar. Taken together with the name - ???milk teeth??? in French - it can be likened to a sensory essay on the transitory process of losing one???s baby teeth.

Jimmy Choo Blossom Perfume by Jimmy Choo, Created in 2015, Jimmy Choo Blossom is a sweet, fruity medley of berries and floral aromas. Wear this as the sun rises high overhead during the spring and summer months. This lovely perfume is distilled happiness in a deep, pink flacon. The top notes are a sugary mixture of raspberry, citrus and red berries. The heart notes make a gentle presentation of sweet pea and rose. The base notes are a smooth collection of sandalwood and musk. Louise Turner crafted this beautiful scent.


Known for his handcrafted shoes, Jimmy Choo learned the trade from his father. Choo took to the craft quickly and was making shoes by himself by age 11. While he was born in Penang, Malaysia, he traveled to England to study and eventually stayed to start a business in London. His first store opened in 1986 and was formerly the site of a hospital. His collections garnered critical acclaim, and he joined with Vogue magazine editor Tamara Mellon to start his personal fashion line in 1996.

Trussardi My Name Perfume by Trussardi, Trussardi My Name by Trussardi is a contemporary blend of floral and vanilla accords. Introduced in 2013, this fragrance is a nod to modern Italian sensibilities. The fragrance opens with powdery violet and vanilla-like heliotrope. Next, the middle notes come out, bringing the scent of lilacs, musk, and lily. The fragrance closes with warm notes of vanilla and amber. This perfume is versatile and can be worn for any occasion.


Trussardi was founded by Dante Trussardi in 1911 as a glove manufacturer. The company saw great success, even becoming the glovemaker for the Royal Family in England. In 1965, his grandson Nicola Trussardi took over the company and propelled it forward. Under Nicola???s leadership, the company expanded its product offerings to include leather jackets, home d‹¨«?®cor, fashion accessories, and more. In the 1980s, the company expanded further, creating fashion lines for men, women, and children, casual wear, eye wear, and fragrances.

Le Participe Passe Perfume by Serge Lutens, Although, the scent was released in 2018, Le Participe Passe, which translates to the past participle,was created in order to evoke feelings of the past. The top notes of artemisia and bergamot are at once floral and a little sharp from the citrus addition. In the middle, more fruit is balanced with the spiciness of pepper. Finally, the base notes of Egyptian balsam and leather anchor the scent, while the additional notes of caramel and cumin evoke familiar smells of sweet treats and the warm comfort of a favorite meal. This is a heavy perfume with long longevity and sillage.

Rihanna Rogue Perfume by Rihanna, Rihanna Rogue is a flirty, feminine fragrance for women. The perfume features a light and floral bouquet of rose, jasmine and cyclamen, along with fruity layers of lemon blossom and plum. Also included in the mix is the leathery and soft aroma of suede. Rounding out this very sexy scent are the deeper base notes of amber, vanilla, musk and patchouli.


Rihanna Rogue became available in 2013. Introduced in 2013 and created by Olivier Cresp and Nathalie Lorson, this fragrance is appealing and striking. The wearer is sure to make a lasting impression wherever she goes. The scent of the blue hour of evening. Porsche Design Pure 22 eau de parfum combines freshness and masculine elegance with woody notes and fruity facets - perfectly capturing the mood when everyday life ends and the evening with friends begins. This multi-faceted men's fragrance has opening notes of spicy cardamom, fresh mandarin, and black pepper. Lavandin, cypriol, and marine accord define the aromatic, sophisticated heart note. The woody-amber base note of cedarwood, cistus, and patchouli round off the signature and create a commanding aura. The composition of the vegan fragrance consists of more than 50% natural materials, essential oils and natural extracts. The bottle, designed by Studio F.A. PORSCHE, reflects the perfume's self-confident elegance and masculine sophistication: translucent, dark blue lacquered glass meets brushed aluminum. The innovative pump mechanism is technically inspired in typical Porsche design: by pressing the spray cap, the aluminum plate glides over the glass as if on rails. A transport clip protects the fragrance when traveling or in your gym bag.

Shahd by Lattafa Perfumes is a Floral Woody Musk fragrance for women. This is a new fragrance. Shahd was launched in 2023. Top notes are Ylang-Ylang and Frangipani; middle notes are Solar Notes and Tuberose; base notes are Musk, Amber, Cedar and Vanilla.
Hayaati Florence by Lattafa Perfumes is a Floral Fruity Gourmand fragrance for women. This is a new fragrance. Hayaati Florence was launched in 2023.

Product_Name: Givenchy Prisme Libre Loose Powder 4 In 1 - 02
Product_Descriptions: A feather-light loose powder that sets the makeup with a final touch. Combines four popular correcting shades in one. Gives a natural, enhanced finish. Incredibly evens out skin tone with shine-control effect. Leaves a perfectly matte yet luminous & translucent complexion

PREP, PROTECT, SET, REFRESH

Introducing the first mist that does it all: Prisme Libre Prep & Set Glow Mist is Givenchy's first primer and setting spray with SPF45 PA++++ protection. A refreshing 4-in-1 mist to prep and protect skin, set and refresh makeup all day long. This latest addition to the Givenchy Prisme Libre face routine creates a pure healthy glow finish. Housed in a handy on-the-go format for a quick and easy gesture, it is the ideal caring protection to be carried everywhere you go

An urban and fast-paced lifestyle, combined with daily external aggression and sun exposure, all contribute to reducing skin radiance. Your skin appears dull and becomes tired-looking, losing its optimal capacity to produce energy and so becoming more impacted by premature aging.

Givenchy's answer? The Skin Perfecto Radiance Perfecting UV Stick SPF 50+ PA++++, for touch-ups anytime, anywhere, to help provide protection against UV rays and display visibly refined-looking skin.

With this on-the-go stick, your skin experiences tri-dimensional perfection, feels revitalized, smoothed and more radiant, while flaws and imperfections seem less visible.

Its iconic pink-and-white marbled signature texture is enriched with iridescent pearls and features an invigorating fragrance for an instant boost.

Boost your eye contour radiance thanks to Givenchy eye care expertise.

Givenchy’s Skin Perfecto Firming and Smoothing Eye Care is a perfecting and anti-aging fluid that provides 360° eye contour improvement¹. The eye contour seems smoother, while the skin looks firmer and embellished with a visibly healthy glow.

Product_Name: Givenchy Rose Perfecto Liquid Lip Balm - 01
Product_Descriptions:
THE FIRST MARBLED COUTURE LIQUID LIP BALM

The enveloping marbled texture of Rose Perfecto Liquid Lip Balm swathes lips in moisturizer-infused color. With 97% skincare ingredients2, its hydrating and comfortable formula is enriched with hyaluronic acid, vitamin C, shea butter, and pink pepper for a nourishing, smoothing, and plumping effect. Day after day, lips are soothed, moisturized, and radiantly healthy.

HYDRATE, PLUMP & NOURISH

Lips are instantly beautified thanks to the immediate plumping effect and ultra-caring creamy texture. Swathed in 24-hour hydration1, the lips are nourished and smoothed.

ICONIC MARBLED SHADES

The new marbled moisturizer formula is infused in color and care to tint the lips with a couture range of fresh shades. The light coverage brings a healthy glossy finish. Iconic shades 001 and 011 adapt to the pH of the lips to create a unique, made-to-measure finish

Product_Name: Givenchy Prisme Libre Loose Powder Travel Size - 5
Product_Descriptions: Givenchy Prisme Libre Loose Powder Travel Size ble designet i 2006 av Nicolas Degennes, Givenchy Makeup and Color Artist Director. Inneholder en harmoni av fire forskjellige nyanser, som matter ned og legger et elegant, lett slør over huden med en nydelig glød. Givenchy presenterer en transparent og strålende finish som holder i opptil seks timer og legger seg lett på huden. Dens ultrafine tekstur gir en naturlig, flott hud. Bak denne lette tekstur, er en unik formula beriket med lysreflekterende pigmenter som garanterer en strålende hud. Dag etter dag vil du oppleve at huden blir mer og mer strålende. De lekre perlepigmentene gir en feilfri look. Hudens tekstur blir utglattet og hudens kvalitet blir synlig forbedret. Pudderet vil sette makeupen din slik at den holder hele dagen. Prisme Libre Loose Powder garanterer et perfekt resultat. Setting-pudderet kommer i seks ulike nyanser slik at det finnes et alternativ fra enhver hudtone, fra den lyseste til den mørkeste.

Product_Name: Givenchy Paris Libre Skin Caring Concealer - C105
Product_Descriptions:
A REVOLUTIONARY CONCEALER

Discover Givenchy Prisme Libre Skin-Caring Concealer, the first 24-hour1 wear 3 multi-purpose concealer of its kind in Givenchy portfolio. Made with 95% natural origin ingredients2, not only does it conceal, correct and unify, it also illuminates and provides 24-hour hydration1 and radiance3.

CORRECT, CARE, ILLUMINATE

With targeted use, Prisme Libre Skin-Caring Concealer instantly corrects and covers, but also blurs dark circles, imperfections and irregularities.

Used all over the face, it evens out the complexion without creasing or settling in fine lines or wrinkles. Skin texture is smoothed from morning to night, the eyes look lifted and signs of fatigue appear reduced. Creating a natural effect, this multi-purpose concealer beautifies the skin with a radiant finish that lasts all day.

Product_Name: Givenchy Le Rouge Interdit Intense Silk Matte Lipstick - 109
Product_Descriptions:
Housed in a rechargeable leather case, Le Rouge Interdit Intense Silk is a timeless and elegant fashion accessory. Its modern texture glides effortlessly over the lips like silk, while delivering a luminous, semi-matte finish. And, thanks to its formula enriched in hyaluronic acid spheres and Acmella Oleracea extract, lips are instantly smoothed and the inner water is locked for up to 24 hours, for absolute comfort. The intense color is impressively long-lasting, staying vibrant for up to 12 hours2.

Combining an ultra-fine film with the most vivid color and the utmost comfort, Le Rouge Interdit Intense Silk redefines the lipstick rules. Less really is more!

Product_Name: Collistar Two Phase Make Up Removing Solution
Product_Descriptions: Collistar Two-Phase Make-Up Removing Solution 150ml is an eye and lip makeup remover that removes even waterproof makeup gently. Enriched with actives that support the skin, it allows a cleansing and care step at the same time. To point out a few, niacinamide contributes to brightening the skin and soothing redness while inulin, a natural prebiotic, contributes to keeping the microbiome of the skin balanced. At the same time, peach blossom extract works to hydrate and soothe the skin while phytic acid shields the skin from pollution. This vegan formula excludes ingredients such as alcohol, fragrance or soap, being incredibly gentle on the skin. Each application impeccably removes all traces of makeup and works to keep the skin balanced and healthy

Product_Name: Collistar Idro Attiva Deep Moisturizing Cream

Product_Descriptions:
A unique treatment combining the multiple benefits of special Italian Thermal Water with the efficacy of the Reprogram System, a unique complex of plant actives, to deliver a targeted, intensive, long-lasting action for visible orange peel skin, fatty deposits and lost skin tone.

THE BENEFITS OF ITALIAN THERMAL WATER

Sourced from the Royal Springs at Valdieri, Piedmont, and enriched with sage extracts, this precious thermal water acts on the surface, toning, compacting and smoothing the skin thanks to its decongesting, antioxidant properties. It also stimulates and reboots the skin’s microcirculation to improve cellular oxigenation.

THE POWER OF THE REPROGRAM SYSTEM

A combination of 5 powerful molecules guarantees an all-round firming, anticellulite action. Targeted Anticellulite Effect The system targets cellulite, orange-peel skin and fatty deposits through a two-fold mechanism that works in synergy:

- reprograms adipocyte metabolism, restoring them to the initial stage of life, preventing lipids from building up inside and triggering the natural “fat burning” mechanism;

- boosts mobilization of lipids within the tissues, encouraging the body’s natural “disposal” process.

Intensive Firming Effect Treats lost tone caused by the tissues hollowing out, stimulating collagen and elastin production and making the skin more compact, for a firmer, more defined body.

GRADUAL RELEASE SHEATH EFFECT

A special natural micro-patch holds the active ingredients in place on the surface of treated areas, without causing occlusion, ensuring they are released gradually and last for much longer.

BIO-STIMULATING MASSAGE ACTION

Creating an immersive wellbeing ritual, the melting, sensory silky texture, with its aromatic marine scent, is delightful to apply and ideal for massages, including professional treatments. To enhance the results, discover Collistar’s exclusive application protocol.

INSTANT AND PROGRESSIVE RESULTS After applying the cream, the skin is instantly softer, smoother and more compact. With continued treatment, the shape of treated areas is gradually remodeled, while orange-peel skin and the ‘spongy’ appearance of cellulite are visibly improved. The contours of the body improve day after day, and the skin is firmer and more toned.

This eye gel essence can be used under or over makeup to instantly counteract the look of dark circles. Immediately, the eye area is hydrated and energized. In 4 weeks, dark circles and puffiness are less visible*. Lightweight texture absorbs quickly without feeling sticky.

La Femme Perfume by Prada, Prada released La Femme in 2016 at the same time they released the masculine LHomme. The fragrance redefines femininity with a unique blend of scents formulated by Daniela Andrier. The opening notes of beeswax and spice give way to heart notes of frangipani, tuberose, iris and ylang ylang. The tuberose is the strongest note, with the frangipani giving it a slightly tropical feel. As the fragrance dries down, the base notes of vanilla and vetiver appear. The beeswax and vanilla give this fragrance a creamy, gourmand accord that reminds you of honey. The combination of white and yellow florals creates a surprisingly sweet floral that the honey vanilla notes balance out perfectly. La Femme has sillage decent and impressive longevity.


Prada was founded in 1913 by Mario Prada. Today, his granddaughter Miuccia runs the fashion empire, which includes clothing, leather goods, perfumes and more. The company released its first scent in 2003

La Femme Prada L'eau Perfume by Prada, La Femme Prada LEau is a lovely everyday floral oriental fragrance that layers light, bright citrus and fresh flowers over a serene base of white woods. Crisp citrus tones of tangerine and mandarin open the scent, tart-sweet and sparkling with effervescent energy. Soft, soothing florals bloom at the heart, fusing creamy tropical accords of Tahitian gardenia and ylang ylang with shimmering white floral nuances of jasmine and tuberose. A quiet finish of blonde wood tempers the lush floralcy of the heart, leaving an enveloping yet ethereal trail that wears close to the skin.


This scent was designed by perfumer Daniela (Roche) Andrier and first released by Italian label Prada in 2017. L???Eau belongs the company???s La Femme collection, launched in 2016. Other fragrances in the series include the green citrus floral scent Water Splash (2019), the floral oriental Velvet Edition (2018), the white floral Intense (2017) and the spicy citrus Absolu (2016).

Prada La Femme by Prada is a Amber Floral fragrance for women. Prada La Femme was launched in 2016. The nose behind this fragrance is Daniela (Roche) Andrier. Top notes are Magnolia, Bergamot and Carrot Seeds; middle notes are Frangipani, Tuberose, Ylang-Ylang, iris and Spices; base notes are Beeswax, Vanilla and Vetiver.

Product_Descriptions:
Mancera Intensitive Aoud Gold Perfume by Mancera, There is an impressive array of notes featured in Mancera Intensitive Aoud Gold perfume. This unisex fragrance really makes a statement, and you will want it around your neck when you want to bring warmth around with you. The opening brings about the sensation of morning dew in addition to Calabrian lemon. The heart contains saffron powder, rose petals, teakwood, geranium leaf and guaiac wood. It finishes strongly with scents of white musk, precious woods and ambergris. This fragrance first entered the market in 2008.


There is much to love about the Mancera brand. Even since the company began in 2008, it has established itself as a niche designer in the industry. The brand house manufactures all of its products using only the best ingredients possible. That is a big reason why each fragrance seems to ooze luxury. Pierre Montale founded the brand and is also the perfumer behind Intensitive Aoud Gold.
Product_Categorise: ['Eau De Parfume Men', 'Eau De Parfume Women', 'Men', 'Women']

Product_Descriptions:
Mancera Intensive Aoud Black Perfume by Mancera, Mancera Intensive Aoud Black is a spicy oriental scent that???s pleasantly warm and perfect for easy-going men and women. The spicy notes are immediately distinctive from the fragrance???s opening: cloves and pepper, with juicy peach to temper them. The heart features an accord curiously reminiscent of Turkish delight, with the scent of roses joined by jasmine, saffron and violet. Finally, the titular oud, or agarwood, forms the rich woody foundation of the perfume along with cedar, sandalwood and gurjan balsam. Designed by Pierre Montale and released in 2008, the scent remains intense and captivating through the day, the spices enriched by the floral and woody notes.


In 2008, Pierre Montale opened Mandera???s first boutique in Paris, tapping into his experiences traveling and studying in the Middle East to establish this sister brand to Montale. Based on refined and luxurious ingredients, his fragrances also draw upon Art Deco inspirations, evident in each starkly stylish bottle designed by Montale???s daughter, Am‹¨«?®lie

Product_Descriptions:
Mancera Black Gold Cologne by Mancera, Fresh spicy and aromatic, Mancera Black Gold was launched in 2017 as a sexy leather fragrance for men, formulated by Pierre Montale. The top notes in this cologne are aromatic and spicy with lavender, cinnamon, nutmeg, citruses, and agarwood (oud). The middle heart notes are violet, rose, jasmine, patchouli leaf, and sea notes. The base is pungent, sensuous, and warm with leather, woody notes, musk, vetiver, and amber. Best worn in cooler weather, this scent is smooth, masculine, long-lasting, and sophisticated.


Founded by perfumer Pierre Montale in 2008, Mancera is a French niche perfume designer that prides itself on using only the best and most luxurious ingredients, guaranteeing a product that is rare and refined. The bottles are all designed with an Art Deco influence, translated into a modern time. With a boutique in the famed Place Vendome in Paris, the brand has more than 50 fragrances to its name.

Product_Descriptions:
Braun Satin Hair 7 ST780 SensoCare Hair Straightener With Automatic Temperature Adaptation

Best known for their specially designed hair care products suitable for all hair types, Braun is a German brand that stands for dependability and quality since 1921.

Their products are used worldwide to improve everyday life.

This Braun SensoCare Hair Straightener comes with an automatic temperature adaptation feature: Sensors present under the ceramic plates actively read the hair's moisture levels and condition. Really small wires connect them to a processor that continuously adjusts temperature 20x per second. Every hair strand is thus protected from heat!

It also comes with an intelligent display that you can personalize, so that it perfectly matches your personal hair type and wants.

Plus the active curling edge is perfect for a wavy or curly look!

Effectively shaves even a strong beard: AutoSense technology detects the shape of your face and adapts to the density of the beard, thanks to which it catches and cuts more beard hairs with each stroke. The lithium-ion battery offers up to three weeks (50 min) of driving time, and a five-minute quick charge is enough for one drive. The shaver is completely waterproof, so it is suitable for both dry and wet shaving. Compatible with the EasyClick system.

The skin around the eyes is delicate and susceptible to damage. Our wrinkle-fighting eye cream is engineered to fortify this skin, making it stronger, visibly smoother, and more resilient.

Longlasting hydration and glow for 100 hours!

Lightweight formula, easily abosrbs into the skin.

Skin Type: Normal, Dry, Combination, and Oily
Skincare Concerns: Dryness, Dullness, and Oiliness

- Aloe Bio-Ferment: Helps infuse skin with moisture.
- Hyaluronic Acid: Helps to create a "moisture reservoir" for ideal hydration.
- Activated Aloe Water: Helps skin absorb moisture more easily.
Ingredient Callouts: Free of parabens and phthalates. It also comes in recyclable packaging.

It contains Auto-Replenishing Technology so skin can create its own internal water source to continually rehydrate itself and then locks in moisture for an endlessly plump-, healthy-looking glow.

Roberto Cavalli Deep Desire Perfume by Roberto Cavalli, Perfume designer Louise Turner launched Roberto Cavalli Deep Desire in 2019. Ideal for evening wear, this sophisticated perfume blends fruity and spicy accords for a luxurious aroma. It opens with a fruity top note of mandarin orange mixed with pink pepper. Heart notes of orange blossom, jasmine and cacao add sweet floralcy that is undercut with just a hit of spiciness. Base notes of patchouli and tonka bean ground the perfume with a subtle smoky accord that is laced with an herbal, earthy undertone. Vanilla adds a creamy gourmand accord. The overall result is an aroma that is both sweet and spicy with a smoky, earthy undertone.

Product_Descriptions:
A flower with a seductive effect.


Wardasina literally means "little rose".

The wonderfully floral fragrance with an oriental character is an elegant homage to the most romantic of flowers. The perfume begins with herbal top notes and Bulgarian rose heart notes. A hint of cedar wood and patchouli give it an earthy aroma. Vanilla, tobacco and musk complete this fragrance experience.

Product_Descriptions:
Ten years after introducing Uden, one of the bestsellers in the Shooting Stars collection, Xerjoff   presents a    powerful new version of the same perfume featuring a richer olfactive pyramid, UDEN OVERDOSE.


Dance upon the waves of the ocean with Uden Overdose, an enchanting fougere fragrance like no other.


Exuding power and strength with every note of Uden Overdose Xerjoff, this perfume is inspired by the tempestuous sea, with enticing top notes of lemon and bergamot.


A dark heart of ginger, tobacco flowers and coffee leads to a rich base note of amber and musk. Uden Overdose is enthroned in a luxurious case embedded with a certified fragment of the meteorite

Product_Descriptions:
A scent which intriguingly evokes mystery with rows of delectable notes beside a warm aura of extravagant woodiness. Symphonium unveils piquant Spanish mandarin and mouth-watering orange juice. Heart-melting and evocative like a poem, Symphonium sings like a chorus of divine voices.


The appetizing citrus accord engages with Indian cardamom which introduces fresh air to the warm Belgian chocolate core. Intensely sweet and deliciously dark, its highly desirable aura is accompanied by voluptuous musk.


A wealthy duet of premium oud woods from Thailand and Laos, and exquisite vanilla from Madagascar enhance the cryptic persona of Symphonium
Product_Categorise: ['Eau De Parfume Men', 'Eau De Parfume Women', 'Men', 'niche', 'Niche Perfumes', 'Women']

Product_Descriptions:
Authentically Italian in heart, body and soul, Renaissance Xerjoff is a sparkling bouquet of fruity accords. Inspired by our rich heritage and an homage to the glamour of our home country.


Renaissance represents the inspiring character of Italy, opening with fresh top notes of Calabrian bergamot, mandarin and lemon. Product_Descriptions:
Pikovaya Dama tells the story of an iconic Russian novel written in the 19th century by Aleksandr Pushkin. Entitled The Queen of Spades, the novel plays a key role in the history of the country and serves as the inspiration for this scent.


Opening with top notes of Calabrian bergamot and neroli, the heart of Pikovaya Dama Xerjoff is a powdery accord of Turkish iris, coriander and Moroccan atlas cedar. Base notes of patchouli, musk and bourbon vanilla provide a warming comfort that reveals itself on the skin as time goes by

Product_Descriptions:
Experience the timeless sophistication of Oesel, a fresh, floral scent underpinned by a warm patchouli and cedar wood base.


Created by Xerjoff's master perfumers, this elegant scent offers a unique take on traditional floral blends, with top notes of zesty lemon and orange flowers leading the nose to a heart of Bulgarian rose, acacia flowers and jasmine sambac.

Refreshing head notes of lemon and verbena are perfectly cooled with a breath of invigorating peppermint. Layers of fresh, green geranium are pitched against fresh and aromatic lavender, while rich notes of cedarwood, sandalwood, oakmoss and ambroxan mingle together to leave a unique, long-lasting arboreal scent for him - a refreshing twist on a classic gentleman's fragrance.


Notes: Lemon, Verbena, Peppermint, Violet Leaves, Iris, Sandalwood, Ambergris


Ingredients: 


Alcool (Alcohol), Parfum (Fragrance), Aqua (Water), Limonene, Linalool, Alpha-Isomethyl Ionone, Hydroxycitronellal, Citral, Geraniol, Citronellol, Benzyl Benzoate, Coumarin.

Product_Descriptions: A fast nail polish dryer that helps prevent smudges and dings. With just a few drops, nails are dry to the touch in 60 seconds and completely dry in less than 2 minutes.

L'Oreal Professionnel Serie Expert Metal Detox Shampoo is a sulfate-free cleanser that gently removes metal particles from the hair. Metal deposits accumulate in everyone's hair; whether it is weak or strong hair, it is not a health issue. The metal level in our hair varies based on the porosity, the water quality in our area, and the erosion of the pipes at home or salons. Metal can lead to hair breakage and significantly contribute to unreliable results during color, balayage, and lightening services. L'Oreal Metal Detox Shampoo is enriched with patented technology consisting of Glicoamine, a small molecule that penetrates deep inside the hair's fiber and targets metal particles. This rich, creamy formula transforms upon contact with water into dense foam that gently removes metal deposits from hair strands. When combined with Pre-Treatment Spray, it reduces hair breakage by 87% while increasing reliable color results to 100%. It delivers a citrus scent with strong musky wood overtones resulting in a one-of-a-kind and enjoyable experience.

An Anti-Oiliness 2-in-1 deep purifier clay. Sebum oxidation and micro cracks on the scalp surface can create oiliness and residue build up. It’s a vicious cycle and you want out.

Concentrated with 6% Clay, the fine-grained active ingredient can do a soft peel on the scalp to help unclog the scalp surface from dirt, oil and sweat.

L'Oréal Professionnel Série Expert Blondifier Gloss Shampoo is a resurfacing and illuminating cleanser to deliver multidimensional shine to blond hair. It gently cleanses the blond hair, removing excess oil, dirt, and impurities while the main ingredient Polyphenol which is present in the açai berry extract provides nourishment and helps to smooth damaged hair. L'Oréal Série Expert Blondifier Gloss Shampoo repairs and smoothes damaged cuticles, and at the same time enhances the multi-dimensional shine of blond hair and leaves it hydrated with vibrant shine.

L'Oréal Professionnel Série Expert Blondifier Masque is specially formulated for natural or chemically treated blond hair. This nourishing mask is loaded with Polyphenols present in the Açai berry extract that replenishes and smooths hair fibers of every strand and revives the natural shine and radiance in blond hair without weighing it down. L'Oréal Blondifier Masque is a great once-a-week treatment for blond hair to enhance resilience and improve overall hair health.

An Anti-hair loss activator serum. Thinning hair and hair loss can be a vicious cycle and you want out.

The Aminexil Advanced Anti-hair loss activator programme was targeted-formulated for hair prone to falling. This lightweight serum helps reduce hair loss.

Concentrated with 1.5% Aminexil to improve collagen and fibronectin network reticulation, reinforcing root anchorage; it is enriched with Omega 6** to help nourish the hair fibre.

L'Oréal Professionnel Série Expert Absolut Repair 10-in-1 Oil is a multipurpose hair oil that offers the hair 10 benefits as soon as applied. This powerful leave-in is the perfect addition to the hair routine of those with damaged hair, regardless of the hair type. It will work on three fronts: as a treatment, protectant, and manageability. First, as a treatment, it will not only nourish and soften the hair but also resurface the hair and reduce split ends. As a result, the hair will have a lightweight touch and feel. On the other hand, the manageability of the hair will be improved. Therefore, the hair will be easier to detangle and blow-dry. Furthermore, this oil helps to control frizz for a polished look all day long. Lastly, this leave-in will provide both anti-pollution and heat protection to up to 230?C/450?F. Moreover, the application in oil form allows for easy distribution to ensure all hair strands will be perfectly coated in this powerful formula. All while providing a luxurious feeling.

Creamy, moisturizing lipstick delivers intense, long-lasting color in a classic, satin finish. Long-wearing formula combines pure plant extracts with intense pigments—so lipstick glides on and stays color-true for hours of flawless wear. Enriched with soothing Mango Oil and Organic Marsh Samphire to plump, comfort, and hydrate lips for 6 full hours.

The House of Creed proudly presents Viking Cologne Eau de Parfum - A bold, fresh fragrance with a real ozonic appearance that complements our original Viking fragrance. This masterful alchemy of dry sandalwood, fresh bergamot, nutmeg and frankincense is inspired by the wild beauty and springtime adventures in the waters of the Norwegian fjords. This aromatic fougère combines the headiness of an eau de parfum with the invigorating freshness of a cologne. A universal fragrance of boundless exploration, Viking Cologne is a contemporary scent for the modern adventurer.


Top notes: Bergamot, lemon, petitgrain, cedarwood
Heart notes: Lavender, patchouli, geranium, vetiver
Base notes: Sandalwood, frankincense, nutmeg, rosemary, sage


Ingredients: 


Alcohol, Parfum (Fragrance), Aqua, Limonene, Ethylhexyl Methoxycinnamate, Ethylhexyl Salicylate, Butyl Methoxydibenzoylmethane, Linalool, Citronellol, Citral, Eugenol, Geraniol, Benzyl Benzoate, Coumarin, Hexyl Cinnamal, Alpha-Isomethyl Ionone, Benzyl Cinnamate, Cinnamyl Alcohol, BHT

Viking Eau de Parfum celebrates the powerful, fearless and fiery modern man. This bold men's fragrance combines fresh citrus notes of Calabrian bergamot and Sicilian lemon with pink peppercorn, Bulgarian rose and peppermint. Woody base notes of Indian Sandalwood and Haitian vetiver complete this masculine masterpiece.


Top notes: Calabrian bergamot Sicilian lemon La Reunion baie rose (pink peppercorn)
Heart notes: Peppercorn Bulgarian rose Peppermint
Base notes: Indian Sandalwood Haitian Vetiver Indian Patchouli Lavandin Absolute


Ingredients: 


Alcool (Alcohol), Parfum (Fragrance), Aqua (Water), Limonene, Linalool, Ethylhexylmethoxycinnamate, Ethylhexyl Salicylate, Butyl Methoxydibenzoylmethane, Eugenol, Coumarin, Citral, Citronellol, Geraniol, Cinnamyl Alcohol, Alpha-Isomethyl Ionone, Farnesol, Benzyl Alcohol, BHT.

Product_Descriptions:
Capturing the aroma of a luxurious smoky cigar, the rich spices of a fine British brandy, and the leather upholstery of a classic British gentleman’s club, Tabarome Millésime Eau de Parfum blends warm and woody notes to create a sophisticated and seductive fragrance for men. Top notes of spicy ginger evolve with gusto thanks to a blend of sandalwood and vetiver. A rich and assertive base, made up of musk and tobacco, offer a lasting masculinity and leathery dry down to this powerhouse perfume. An ideal choice for the leaders of the pack.


Top notes: Bergamot, lemon, mandarin, ginger
Heart notes: Jasmine, sandalwood, vetiver
Base notes: Musk, tobacco, tea


Ingredients: 


Alcool (Alcohol), Parfum (Fragrance), Aqua (Water), Alpha-Isomethyl Ionone, Linalool, Limonene, Coumarin, Citral, Geraniol, Isoeugenol, Eugenol, Citronellol, Hydroxycitronellal.

Product_Descriptions:
Unlike other vetiver offerings, The House of Creed uses both the leaves and the roots in this signature men's fragrance, providing a new and unique interpretation of this mythical ingredient. A green and fresh masculine scent, Original Vétiver Eau de Parfum also retains the earthy and leathery characteristics of the complete vetiver plant. A truly contemporary interpretation of a traditional Vetiver perfume for men, Original Vétiver's rich and woody base is complemented by uplifting notes of citrus and a burst of the fresh outdoors thanks to the signature vetiver leaves, creating a scent reminiscent of a lingering summer.


Top notes: Bergamot, bitter orange, mandarin, vetiver leaves
Heart notes: White pepper, coriander, pink pepper
Base notes: Mysore sandalwood, vetiver, ambergris, tonkin musk


Ingredients:

Product_Descriptions: "Slender blue palm trees sway in the musky wind, as oil of vetiver stirs under a canopy of white flowers. Swallows wildly sweep across the leather, skimming over the ground. Product_Descriptions:
As part of the Creed Royales Exclusives collection, Spice and Wood is the luxury asset hand made for men  but also intensely enjoyed by women.
With Spice and Woods depth and power, sixth generation master perfumer Olivier Creed celebrates the House of Creeds long history of creating fragrance of great aesthetic value. Les Royales Exclusives collection is one of the most ambitious projects in Creeds 250 years, a statement to the creative world about the legacy, quality and collectability of fragrance as art.


Woody-Spicy / Fresh


Strength refined and power honed are the hallmarks of Creed Spice and Wood. Rich with natural treasures of the East and Europe, Spice and Wood is fit for wear in the competitive places of a mans life and in his realms of celebration, from concert hall to holiday fete.


Notes
Top note: Bergamot, essence of sun-drenched lemons and aromatic apples from Italy
Middle note: Angelica root, oil of cloves, desert peppers, heady patchouli, a hint of white birch
Base note: Egyptian iris and pungent cedar, oak moss and finest musk for depth

Ingredients: Alcool (Alcohol), Parfum (Fragrance), Aqua (Water), Linalool, Limonene, Alpha-Isomethyl Ionone, Hydroxycitronellal, Coumarin, Citronellol, Citral, Farnesol, Geraniol, Cinnamal, Benzyl Benzoate, Methyl 2-Octynoate.

During the daytime, our skin uses its energy to protect itself.


All Day All Year is the perfect daycare product, supporting the skin by acting as a global protective shield, to keep the skin looking younger. When designing All Day All Year, Sisley’s Laboratories studied the internal and environmental factors to which we are exposed over our lives. These factors are grouped together under the scientific term exposome, which encompasses pollution and cigarette smoke in particular. They are responsible for 80% of skin aging.


The complex and highly concentrated formula of All Day All Year protects the skin from aggressors that can cause premature aging and enhance its self-defense* power thanks to two complementary physical and biological shields. On the surface of the skin, the physical shield, with its encapsulated filters, provides comprehensive protection against pollutants to limit their penetration into the skin**. Within the skin, the biological shield stimulates its natural defenses by: - helping to strengthen the skin barrier - activating the skin’s self-defense* capabilities to limit the harmful effects of pollutants** - providing an anti-aging action.

Product_Name: Pupa Made To Last Extreme Fluid Foundation - 001-Light Ivory
Product_Descriptions:
A super long lasting, total comfort foundation that never lets you down.
Born to last in time and weather resistant, for a perfect make-up result even with humidity and high temperatures*. Its texture is fresh and melt-on, it blends homogeneously on the skin. The result? A perfect face skin all day long. Adjustable coverage from medium to high.
6 shades available.
*Clinical trial carried out by a dermatologist on 30 women. Color resistance was instrumentally assessed on 10 women also after exposure to high temperatures and high levels of humidity.
Suitable for all skin types
SPF 10 – SPF 30
Low risk of allergies
Dermatologist tested
Non comedogenic
Paraben free
Oil free
Fragrance free
Alcohol free

Product_Name: Adidas  Get Ready Male Roll On - 50Ml
Product_Descriptions: Adidas get ready. Roll-on deodorant embodies a unique blend of joy, dance and freedom. The woody aromatic fragrance exudes lust for life and perfectly complements daily body care. The lightweight composition with pleasantly dosed intensity is suitable for both sports and everyday use. The men's fragrance is a tropical blend of fresh fruits with natural aromas and spicy woods. The top note symbolically represents the Brazilian colours of green mandarin, yellow pineapple and blue sea breeze. The middle note offers a natural combination of exotic fruits with aromatic notes of clary sage and fresh lavender, while the base is rounded off with cedar, intense sandalwood and male patchouli. adidas get ready. gives energy and joie de vivre to enjoy every day in its fullness - ideal for energetic men.

Moschino Pink Fresh Couture Perfume by Moschino, The first thing shoppers are sure to notice about Moschino Pink Fresh Couture is its interestingly ironic packaging. However, this Moschino creation has much more to offer than just an original exterior. The contents contain a one-of-a-kind fragrance that???s well-liked among perfume aficionados worldwide. The top notes include black currant, pink grapefruit and lily-of-the-valley. The core notes consist of pomegranate, pink hyacinth and heady rose. Base notes of ambroxan, cedar and musk wrap up the experience and add a bit of smoothness to the otherwise sweet mixture.


Moschino was founded as a design house by Franco Moschino in 1983. The company quickly became known for its colorful designs, almost all of which introduced some form of social commentary. In 1987, the brand introduced its first signature fragrance, a part of a huge branching-out that led the company to introduce leather goods, cosmetics, jewelry and even a hotel in 2001.


Moschino Pink Fresh Couture has a soft sillage despite the number of notes involved in the mixture, and offers a very long-lasting wear time.

Product_Name: Moschino Cheap And Chic So Real - 100ML
Product_Descriptions:
Cheap & Chic So Real Perfume by Moschino, A light, floral, and fruity fragrance that was launched in 2017, Cheap & Chic So Real for women is a fun scent good for everyday wear. The top notes open with a fruity, but still complex bouquet of bitter orange, tangerine, raspberry, and black currant. The middle notes bring in the sensual and heady floral notes of pink peony, jasmine, and magnolia. At the base, oak moss, cedar, and musk give the scent enough depth to keep it fun instead of frivolous. The sillage and longevity are both moderate which means it can be applied often and with a heavy hand if so desired.


Moschino is an Italian fashion house that was started in 1983. It is known for its fun, colorful designs and colors. This perfume matches that aesthetic in its scent as well as its packaging. The tall bottle is covered in a design of flowers, lips, and long-lashed eyes. The top of the bottle even boasts a face that appears to be winking at you with one eye covered by a sunflower.

Missoni Cologne by Missoni, Missoni is a cologne for men that was launched in 2017. It is a versatile fragrance that can fit any occasion and season. Remnant of the Mediterranean climate, the men???s fragrance captures the Italian coast in its scent.

Roberto Cavalli Nero Assoluto Perfume by Roberto Cavalli, Roberto Cavalli Nero Assoluto is an oriental floral fragrance for women by Roberto Cavalli. Introduced in 2012, it is a simple but powerful perfume that has the ability to adapt to any occasion. This fragrance opens with zesty notes of citrus fruit and powdery sweet notes of orchid. At the heart of this perfume is vanilla, in all its warm, cozy, gourmand glory. The fragrance closes with a base note of ebony, which smells woody, but with a slightly darker twist.


Roberto Cavalli is a luxury Italian fashion design house, founded by Roberto Cavalli in 1970. Born to an artistic family, the young Cavalli studied art, and textile printing in particular. He debuted his fashion line in Paris in 1970 and opened his own atelier soon afterward. The company is known for its exotic and glamorous looks and its prevalent use of colorful silks, animal prints, leather and denim. The fashion house now sells womenswear, menswear, fragrance and vodka. It released its first fragrance in 2002

Product_Name: Nivea Visage Q10 Night Cream Energy - 50Ml
Product_Descriptions:
At night, the processes of cell division, production and recovery of what was destroyed during the day are accelerated. So when it comes to nighttime skincare, try the Nivea Q10 Energy Recharging Night Cream. The night cream gives you more radiant skin and a healthy appearance for eight hours. Helps reduce the first signs of aging. This cream combines three powerful antioxidants - Q10, vitamin C and vitamin E, which recharge, regenerate and deeply nourish the skin. This anti-aging night cream nourishes tired skin, visibly reducing fine lines and the first signs of wrinkles. The formula improves the moisture retention of the skin.

While you sleep, the night cream works visibly to reduce signs of fatigue for skin that looks fresh and energized in the morning.

Skin tolerance dermatologically proven. Contains 0% alcohol.

Reve D'infini Perfume by Lalique, Introduced in 2015, Reve D'infini is a floral woody musk women???s perfume with fruity, floral, musky, woody, rose, and fresh spicy main accords. Best for spring and summer day wear, this fragrance has moderate sillage and longevity. Top notes of bergamot, litchi, and white rose open this work, with freesia, jasmine, rose, peach, and cedar in the center. Vanilla, musk, and sandalwood base notes close this performance. Perfumer Richard Ibanez of Robertet is the nose behind this scent.


Lalique is the glass design house founded by French artist, jeweler, and ceramist Rene Lalique in 1885. His first jewelry pieces emphasized design, depicting animals and the female form. He turned to glassware, where he found his greatest success. He collaborated with Francois Coty to create perfume bottles for Coty???s fragrances and designed a manufacturing process to produce bottles on a large scale. The first fragrances for the brand were not released until 1992, when the founder???s granddaughter, Marie-Claude, worked with Art & Fragrance to create new perfumes in sculptural bottles.

An Eau de Parfum inspired by Olivier's family travels around the Mediterranean ocean, Erolfa is a fresh, crisp and versatile signature scent, that will carry you effortlessly through from morning to evening. Bergamot, mandarin, ginger and basil intrigue the senses, giving way to a burst of herbal freshness conjured up by a blend of lavender, coriander, watermelon, cucumber and jasmine. Sandalwood, cedarwood and musk form a lasting and sophisticated base of this uplifting and aromatic fragrance. Equally invigorating and comforting, Erolfa will transport you to a salty sunbaked boat deck in the heat of summer.


Top notes: Bergamot, lemon, orange, violet, cumin, basil, rosemary, melon
Heart notes: Cyclamen, jasmine, ginger, coriander, pepper
Base notes: Cedarwood, sandalwood, oakmoss, amber musk


Ingredients: 


Alcool (Alcohol), Parfum (Fragrance), Aqua (Water), Limonene, Linalool, Citral, Alpha-Isomethylionone, Geraniol, Eugenol, Citronellol, Benzyl Benzoate, Isoeugenol.

Top notes: Bergamot, lemon, mandarin, verbena, clementine, peppermint

Product_Descriptions: Iris Tubereuse Perfume by Creed, Iris Tubereuse, released in 2014, is a youthful, optimistic perfume with a refined essence. Dazzling and bright, it is sure to capture attention. The complex opening features violet leaf, galbanum, and orange. Each ingredient offers its own sweetness, while lending floral, green, and citrus notes. The middle is distinctly floral, making beautiful use of lily, lily of the valley, and tuberose. Their fresh, intoxicating aromas fill out the fragrance
A very nice and soft fragrance for ladies and gentlemen! We think this is the lightest fragrance from Creed's acqua original range. Olivier found the fragrances in the forests of Virginia.

Product_Descriptions: It is Master Perfumer Olivier Creed's living fragrance journal of countless globetrotting journeys with the fine art of perfumery as the narrative. The Island of Java, Olivier's favorite destination east of Bali and just south of the equator, served as inspiration for Vetiver Geranium. The accord brings to life Indonesian vetiver that adorns the mountainous rolling hills of its native landscape and pairs the sensual, soothing essence of geranium to create a vibrant juice. Handpicked crisp granny smith apple, bergamot and lemon make a luminous debut, while warm cinnamon and rose lead to hearty patchouli, cedar and relaxing amber.

Product_Descriptions: Aberdeen Lavander Perfume by Creed, Creed introduced Aberdeen Lavander in 2014 to add to its Oriental Fougere collection. Rosemary, artemisia, bergamot and lemon top notes start the scent off with herbal touches and a citrus edge. This dissipates into a floral bouquet of middle notes dominated by its namesake scent, lavender. Rounding out the heart are subtle glimpses of rose and lily

Product_Name: Creed Aqua Originale Asian Green Tea - 100Ml
Product_Descriptions: Creed Asian Green Tea, eau de parfum 100 ml belongs to the Acqua Originale Collection which is Master Perfumer Olivier Creed’s living fragrance journal of countless globetrotting journeys with the fine art of perfumery as the narrative. Born from Olivier’s appreciation of Japanese art and culture of the Far East, Asian Green Tea opens with green, golden notes evoking the landscape of Malaysia, one of his favorite Eastern destinations. The fragrance bows with sparkling bergamot, mandarin and essential oil of lemon petitgrain, then uncovers a fragrant floral bouquet of violet, heliotrope, rose and sweet cassie blended with the region’s ritual –green tea. The finish is a warm melange of amber, sandalwood and musk.

With Patchouli Ardent, Thierry Wasser, Guerlains master Perfumer, has reinvented patchouli, a raw material usually darkly woody and mysterious, in a surprisingly vibrant and bright way. It combines the elegance of Rose with a majestic leather and musks accord to offer a unique sensorial voyage. Woody Floral.
Captivating, bright, elegant.
Patchouli, Rose and Musks

Prime and line lips for perfect definition with 8 hour wear.

Prime: Glides on seamlessly with a balm-like texture that helps lock in hydration. Prepares lips for color, and ensures smooth application.

Line: A long lasting lip liner to enhance or correct your lip shape for a perfectly defined look. The automatic pencil lines, defines and precisely fills your lips with color. Glides on smoothly and effortlessly to shape, shade, or color lips.

Weightless comfort. Bold color payoff. Matte finish.

HOW TO USE

Prepare your lips for color by applying the primer. This will help lock in moisture and smooth your lips to hold both the liner and lipstick in place.

Next, trace your natural lip contour with the liner to define lips. Begin at the center and work outward for a precise application.

For a matte finish, continue using the liner to fill in the lips, or apply your favorite shade of ModernMatte Powder Lipstick, VisionAiry GelLipstick or another lipstick or your choice.

For a glossy look, apply Crystal GelGloss or Shimmer GelGloss.

Product_Name: Shiseido Synchro Skin Self Refreshing Tint - 115
Product_Descriptions: A fresh, weightless skin tint that synchronizes with skin to provide light coverage, balancing skin texture and tone, while letting your natural skin shine through. Featuring ActiveForce™ technology, which actively resists heat & humidity, oil and motion, this tinted moisturizer self-refreshes nonstop for a fresh, natural finish that lasts all day. This hybrid formula contains 70% skincare ingredients including Hyaluronic Acid to deliver an instant burst of hydration and hydrated, nourished skin for 24 hours. Shades are flexible to work across different skin tones. Available in 12 shades.

Product_Name: Lancome Renergie Yeux Multi-Lift ultra Eye Cream - 15Ml
Product_Descriptions:
Triple Anti-ageing effect for a younger looking eye contour.
Lancôme Laboratories discovered eyes are the most demanding area that reveals your age and introduce our first Lifting Filler Eye Cream, featuring next-generation Hyaluronic Acid Ultra-Filler. This product targets 3 major signs of ageing: lift sagginess, improve the appearance of wrinkles and even brighten dark circles under eyes.
Formulated with next-generation Hyaluronic Acid, the filling effect of this anti aging eye cream treats the most demanding area: your eye contours.
The product combines our Linseed extract exclusively sourced in France and obtained with a French biotech process, in a silky-smooth texture, this eye wrinkle cream shows clinically proven multi-efficacy:
Instant Moisture
8-week lifting on eye contours
And now -15% on dark circles*
Recommended for all skintypes.

Vetiver Oriental Perfume by Serge Lutens, Christopher Sheldrake is the nose behind this 2004 woodsy aroma by Serge Lutens. Vetiver Oriental is a powerful earthy fragrance that is daring in its unique scent pairings. The perfume opens with delicate top notes of iris; blooms into the heart notes of vetiver, Guaiac wood, and dark chocolate; and finally soothes into base notes of amber, sandalwood, labdanum, and musk.


Lutens was born in France in 1942 and started his career as a hair stylist before moving into cosmetics and photography. In the 1960s he joined Vogue magazine in Paris as a makeup artist and was commissioned to create his own line of cosmetics by CD in 1967. In the 1970s, Lutens focus turned towards photography, and he directed two short films that were screened at the Cannes Film Festival. It was not until 2000 that the artist launched a line of perfumes, many of which are niche fragrances, highly unique in their unusual compositions.

This upgraded rich cream-gel delivers an instant moisture boost, then keeps skin continuously hydrated for 72 hours—even after washing your face. With barrier-strengthening lipids and soothing cica. Oil-free.

EGE by Nishane is a Aromatic Spicy fragrance for women and men. This is a new fragrance. EGE  was launched in 2020. The nose behind this fragrance is Ilias Ermenidis. Top notes are violet leaves, Yuzu and Anise; middle notes are Basil, Mint and Cardamom; base notes are Licorice and Olibanum.

Colognise by Nishane is a Citrus fragrance for women and men. Colognise was launched in 2018. Top notes are Bergamot, Green Tea, Jasmine and Lemon; middle notes are Grapefruit and Lily-of-the-Valley; base notes are Neroli, Vetiver and Musk.

B-612 by Nishane is a Woody Aromatic fragrance for women and men. B-612 was launched in 2018. The nose behind this fragrance is Chris Maurice. Top notes are Cypress, Lavender and Geranium; middle notes are Cashmeran, Cedar, Sandalwood and Patchouli; base notes are Musk, Oakmoss and Tonka Bean.

Product_Name: Bassam Fattouh Nostalgie D'Orient+ Kohl+Lipstick - Lipstick

Product_Name: Collistar Magnifica Replumping Cream Face & Neck
Product_Descriptions: Collistar’s iconic, ultimate anti-age cream is now even more effective. It contains a special Sesame Seed Extract to stimulate the natural process of adipoge+C28nesis, visibly replumping the skin. Thanks to a clever combination of two next-generation peptides and an encapsulated plant cholesterol, it redensifies the epidermis and restores the skin’s barrier function, boosting its natural ability to repair itself. Deep wrinkles are drastically reduced. The rich texture melts instantly into the skin. For all skin types, including sensitive skin.

Product_Name: Collistar Magnifica Redensifyng Eye Contour Cream
Product_Descriptions: Rich and velvety, it brings youth to the eye contour area. The formula contains Gamma Aminobutyric Acid, for a reduction of eyes wrinkles. In synergy with exclusive Chaga Mushroom extract, it helps reduce dark circles and minimize lines and signs of tiredness. Also suitable for sensitive eyes.

Product_Name: Collistar Magnifica Light Replumping Cream Face & Neck
Product_Descriptions: All the powerful effects of Collistar’s ultimate anti-age cream in a new, ultra-light texture. It contains a special Sesame Seed Extract to stimulate the natural process of adipogenesis, visibly replumping the skin. Thanks to a clever combination of two next-generation peptides and an encapsulated plant cholesterol, it redensifies the epidermis and restores the skin’s barrier function, boosting its natural ability to repair itself. Deep wrinkles are drastically reduced. The non-heavy, ultra-soft texture makes it perfect for normal and combination skin. Also suitable for sensitive skin.

Product_Name: Collistar Anticellulite Cryo Gel Boosted Formula
Product_Descriptions: A new combination of active ingredients for a global anticellulite strategy. - Cold effect. Inspired by cryotherapy, the formula gives an immediate sensation of lightness, particularly in the legs. - Aromatherapy effects. The essential oils stimulate vitality and wellbeing. - Boosted lifting effect. A blend of plant-based alpha-hydroxy acids instantly lifts the skin and minimizes imperfections. Centella Asiatica combats loss of elasticity and ensures a progressive lifting action. - Boosted anticellulite action on the causes behind the problem: the buildup of localized fat and alterations of microcirculation. Two powerful active ingredients (Pink pepper and Caffeine) act on fat deposits at three levels, • limiting the formation of mature adipocytes (fat cells) • preventing new lipids from accumulating • helping get rid of existing fat. Draining, vasoprotective plant extracts - pineapple, horse chestnut and blueberry - combined with an innovative, flavonoid-rich fermented green coffee extract stop liquids from building up. Its unmistakable gel texture is light, fresh and quickly absorbed. For all skin types. * cosmetic against the imperfections caused by cellulite.

Skin becomes visibly refined while the appearance of fine lines and wrinkles are diminished. Skin feels dewy, soft and fully moisturized. Skin feels dewy and soft while the cream works to diminish the appearance of fine lines and wrinkles.

Fragrance Black XS EDP perfume for Women by Paco Rabanne was released in 2018. Who Is It Best For? Well it is an aroma highlighted by a bouquet of fragrant woody, powdery and sweet scented tones that will bring a sensual, warm and inviting perfumed sensation. Examining it closer once applied you will notice a lingering quality of softer fragranced bitter, floral and spicy sweet hints that hide an essence of uplifting, bright and soft feelings.


Based on the combination of notes Paco Rabanne Black XS EDP is classified as Oriental Woody fragrance to the nose. The emanation of flavors and scent notes for Black XS EDP unfurl in a whiff of spice and fruity opening top notes including cranberry, pink pepper and tamarind. The floral and spice heart center notes blend in with cacao while the deep woody and spice base notes leave an impression of woody.

Beach Hut Woman by Amouage is a Woody Aquatic fragrance for women. Beach Hut Woman was launched in 2018. Top notes are Mineral notes and Bergamot; middle notes are Driftwood and Ylang-Ylang; base notes are Patchouli and Cashmeran.

Top notes are Marigold, Ginger, Grapefruit and Bergamot; middle notes are Incense, Walnut, Immortelle, Kiwi, Honey, Opoponax, Coffee, Sandalwood, Rose, Orange Blossom and Jasmine; base notes are Leather, Benzoin, Agarwood (Oud), Sandalwood, Tonka Bean, Amber, Oakmoss, Vanilla and Musk.

Fate for Men by Amouage is a Oriental Spicy fragrance for men. Fate for Men was launched in 2013. Top notes are Cumin, Saffron, Wormwood, Ginger and Mandarin Orange; middle notes are Immortelle, Incense, Copahu Balm, Olibanum, Labdanum and Rose; base notes are Licorice, Labdanum, Sandalwood, Cedar, Musk and Tonka Bean.

Jubilation 25 Woman by Amouage is a Oriental Floral fragrance for women. Jubilation 25 Woman was launched in 2008. The nose behind this fragrance is Lucas Sieuzac. Top notes are Ylang-Ylang, Rose, Tarragon and Lemon; middle notes are Incense, Rose, Labdanum and Artemisia; base notes are Myrrh, Amber, Vetiver, Patchouli and Musk.

Myths Woman by Amouage is a Floral Green fragrance for women. Myths Woman was launched in 2016. Top notes are Chrysanthemum, Narcissus, Violet Leaf and Labdanum; middle notes are Carnation, Ambergris and Patchouli; base notes are Moss, Leather and Musk.
